<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 10:08:32 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>五年内，以色列纳税人为内塔尼亚胡儿子的安全花费了 2150 万谢克尔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/security-for-netanyahus-family-cost-israeli-taxpayers-21-5-million-shekels-in-five-years/00000190-c4c4-d3e0-a5fd-eff5f8f20000</link><description>根据信息自由请求公开的信息显示，过去五年来，以色列为内塔尼亚胡妻子和两个儿子的安全花费了 2150 万谢克尔。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 09:28:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/security-for-netanyahus-family-cost-israeli-taxpayers-21-5-million-shekels-in-five-years/00000190-c4c4-d3e0-a5fd-eff5f8f20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军证实击毙了黎巴嫩哈马斯指挥官，他对以色列发射火箭弹负有责任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article-live/mossad-chief-urges-gaza-deal-says-netanyahus-cease-fire-terms-could-nix-hostage-release/00000190-c3bc-d3a7-a79e-c3ff79830000</link><description>圣殿山上的极右翼部长本格维尔：祈祷反对“鲁莽”的人质交易 ■ 摩萨德主席敦促加沙达成协议，称内塔尼亚胡的停火条款可能会阻止人质释放 ■ 在甘茨的支持下，以色列议会通过了反对巴勒斯坦建国的决议 ■ 两辆汽车遭到袭击在黎巴嫩</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 02:56:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article-live/mossad-chief-urges-gaza-deal-says-netanyahus-cease-fire-terms-could-nix-hostage-release/00000190-c3bc-d3a7-a79e-c3ff79830000</guid></item><item><title>‘哪里有愤怒？这是对美国人的攻击：美以人质奥马尔·诺伊特拉的父母呼吁共和党人支持</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/parents-of-american-israeli-hostage-campus-antisemitism-star-at-rnc-foreign-policy-night/00000190-c39a-d2f8-abdb-e7fef62b0000</link><description>在大会的外交政策晚会上，题为“让美国再次强大”的晚会以哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击以色列的镜头开始，罗南和奥娜·诺伊特拉带领代表们高呼“带他们回家”，而其他发言者则攻击拜登的中东政策以及美国校园的“反西方、反美、反犹太”氛围</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 02:20:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/parents-of-american-israeli-hostage-campus-antisemitism-star-at-rnc-foreign-policy-night/00000190-c39a-d2f8-abdb-e7fef62b0000</guid></item><item><title>在甘茨的支持下，以色列议会通过反对巴勒斯坦建国的决议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/knesset-passes-resolution-against-establishment-of-palestinian-state/00000190-c2c6-d13a-ad92-caffa4b90000</link><description>该声明指出，“巴勒斯坦国将对以色列国及其公民构成生存威胁。”它得到了 68 名议会议员的支持，只有 9 名议员反对，全部来自阿拉伯政党</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 22:43:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/knesset-passes-resolution-against-establishment-of-palestinian-state/00000190-c2c6-d13a-ad92-caffa4b90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会提出法案，允许以色列警方在没有证据的情况下限制公民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-bill-would-let-police-restrict-citizens-based-solely-on-intel-gathered-by-cops/00000190-c29c-d2f8-abdb-e6fca6a10000</link><description>以色列议会国家安全委员会提出了一项极右翼成员的法案，他表示该法案将为警察提供打击阿拉伯社会犯罪的工具。司法部反对该法律并正在制定自己的版本</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 21:49:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-bill-would-let-police-restrict-citizens-based-solely-on-intel-gathered-by-cops/00000190-c29c-d2f8-abdb-e6fca6a10000</guid></item><item><title>共和党大会外交政策之夜预计将对拜登的以色列和伊朗政策进行攻击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/the-attacks-on-bidens-israel-iran-policies-to-expect-at-gop-convention/00000190-c257-db81-a3f7-f2dfea710000</link><description>共和党人将攻击总统在中东、以色列和伊朗问题上的记录，并将听取以色列裔美国人质奥马尔·诺伊特拉父母的意见</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 20:49:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/the-attacks-on-bidens-israel-iran-policies-to-expect-at-gop-convention/00000190-c257-db81-a3f7-f2dfea710000</guid></item><item><title>新调查发现，四分之一的以色列犹太人愿意离开以色列前往另一个国家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/one-in-four-israeli-jews-would-leave-israel-if-they-could-new-survey-finds/00000190-c202-d3e0-a5fd-ebb7ad1e0000</link><description>根据犹太人民政策研究所的最新月度调查，近一半的以色列阿拉伯公民表示，如果有实际机会，他们会移民。 30% 的受访者表示他们更喜欢拜登，24% 的人更喜欢特朗普</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 19:44:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/one-in-four-israeli-jews-would-leave-israel-if-they-could-new-survey-finds/00000190-c202-d3e0-a5fd-ebb7ad1e0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在 10 月 7 日的失败中装傻了。别相信他</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-17/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahu-is-playing-dumb-on-his-october-7-failures-dont-believe-him/00000190-c1e5-d258-a3ff-e5ed94dd0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡已竭尽全力避免政府对 10 月 7 日发生的情报、行动和领导失误进行正式调查，让他可以自由地编造自己的故事 — — 并逃避责任</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 19:32:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-17/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahu-is-playing-dumb-on-his-october-7-failures-dont-believe-him/00000190-c1e5-d258-a3ff-e5ed94dd0000</guid></item><item><title>美国禁止因杀害巴勒斯坦袭击者而被定罪的以色列士兵入境</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/u-s-bans-entry-for-idf-soldier-convicted-of-killing-incapacitated-palestinian-assailant/00000190-c1d3-d13a-ad92-c9fb56490000</link><description>对前以色列国防军士兵埃洛尔·阿扎里亚及其家人的签证禁令可能是以色列首次因法外处决而被指定，开创了一个新的先例，可能会产生巨大的影响</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 18:37:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/u-s-bans-entry-for-idf-soldier-convicted-of-killing-incapacitated-palestinian-assailant/00000190-c1d3-d13a-ad92-c9fb56490000</guid></item><item><title>“诺亚，他在利用你”：家人准备抗议内塔尼亚胡的国会演讲，恳求获救人质不要加入</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/families-prepare-to-protest-netanyahu-congress-speech-urging-rescued-hostage-not-to-join/00000190-c16a-d258-a3ff-e5eb96900000</link><description>人质亲属敦促诺亚·阿加马尼及其家人拒绝陪同总理在国会发表讲话的邀请。一位亲戚说，“我们会发现自己处于抗议你的荒谬境地，我们不希望这样”</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 17:48:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/families-prepare-to-protest-netanyahu-congress-speech-urging-rescued-hostage-not-to-join/00000190-c16a-d258-a3ff-e5eb96900000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 285 天：议会拒绝组建 10 月 7 日国家调查委员会的法案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-285-knesset-rejects-bill-to-form-oct-7-state-commission-of-inquiry/00000190-c19e-d258-a3ff-e59fd19a0000</link><description>以色列议会否决了一项关于成立国家委员会调查 10 月 7 日事件的法案。 ■ 真主党领袖哈桑·纳斯拉拉 (Hassan Nasrallah) 威胁称，如果以色列国防军加强对黎巴嫩平民的袭击，他们将向以色列更深处发动袭击。至少九人 ■ 以色列人质的表弟敦促诺亚·阿加马尼不要与内塔尼亚胡一起飞往华盛顿 ■ 战争进入 285 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 17:10:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-285-knesset-rejects-bill-to-form-oct-7-state-commission-of-inquiry/00000190-c19e-d258-a3ff-e59fd19a0000</guid></item><item><title>利库德集团部长和沙斯呼吁内塔尼亚胡在极右翼反对下达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/netanyahu-minister-far-right-smotrich-must-be-fired-for-opposing-hostage-deal/00000190-c157-d3a7-a79e-c357c25f0000</link><description>摩萨德负责人警告以色列内阁部长，内塔尼亚胡坚持加沙协议的某些条件可能会阻止人质获释，敦促政府朝着加沙休战迈进</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 16:54:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/netanyahu-minister-far-right-smotrich-must-be-fired-for-opposing-hostage-deal/00000190-c157-d3a7-a79e-c357c25f0000</guid></item><item><title>最高法院批评以色列军队利用“封闭军事区”来防止约旦河西岸定居者与巴勒斯坦人之间的冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/top-court-criticizes-idf-for-using-closed-military-zones-to-prevent-west-bank-clashes/00000190-c0f2-d3a7-a79e-c2f3d7eb0000</link><description>法院要求该州提供有关发布关闭令的数量、发布关闭令的说明以及宣布关闭军事区的情况的数据。一名法官表示，数百起此类案件表明以色列国防军认为这是一个“神奇的解决方案”</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 15:29:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/top-court-criticizes-idf-for-using-closed-military-zones-to-prevent-west-bank-clashes/00000190-c0f2-d3a7-a79e-c2f3d7eb0000</guid></item><item><title>战争尚未结束，但这些以色列家庭已经返回黎巴嫩边境的家园</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/displaces-israeli-families-return-home-to-the-north-despite-ongoing-war/00000190-c04f-de8b-adfc-d96f51dc0000</link><description>在酒店度过了漫长的几个月后，疏散的家庭并没有期待恢复正常，但他们回到家时却面临着可怕的现实</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 13:26:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/displaces-israeli-families-return-home-to-the-north-despite-ongoing-war/00000190-c04f-de8b-adfc-d96f51dc0000</guid></item><item><title>“措施升级”：内塔尼亚胡和加兰特的分歧在人质谈判中达到顶峰</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/an-escalation-of-measures-netanyahu-gallants-rift-peaks-amid-hostage-talks/00000190-bf84-de8b-adfc-bfa43d5a0000</link><description>即使是内塔尼亚胡联盟中最极右翼的成员也认为他的政策只是另一个伎俩，旨在挫败任何协议。官员们认为，如果内塔尼亚胡确实挫败了这笔交易，加兰特将再次面对公众对他发出警告</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 11:42:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/an-escalation-of-measures-netanyahu-gallants-rift-peaks-amid-hostage-talks/00000190-bf84-de8b-adfc-bfa43d5a0000</guid></item><item><title>据报道内塔尼亚胡称人质“遭受痛苦，但没有死亡”，家人要求澄清</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/hostage-families-want-answers-after-pm-reportedly-says-theyre-suffering-not-dying/00000190-c05e-d211-a5da-ed5fd8350000</link><description>人质家庭论坛总部表示，内塔尼亚胡的言论“事实上不准确，而且非常不负责任”</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 11:34:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/hostage-families-want-answers-after-pm-reportedly-says-theyre-suffering-not-dying/00000190-c05e-d211-a5da-ed5fd8350000</guid></item><item><title>经过九个月的战争后，哈马斯在加沙内外有多受欢迎？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-07-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-popular-is-hamas-in-gaza-and-outside-of-it-after-nine-months-of-war/00000190-bfda-d211-a5da-ffdbea210000</link><description>最近对哈马斯支持率的民意调查各不相同，但明显的趋势是巴勒斯坦人之间的差距不断扩大，这取决于他们居住的地方和他们的经历。以下是哈马斯在加沙支持率下降的原因，以及为什么哈马斯的“抵抗”在西岸、巴勒斯坦侨民和亲巴勒斯坦盟友中仍被积极看待</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 11:15:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-07-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-popular-is-hamas-in-gaza-and-outside-of-it-after-nine-months-of-war/00000190-bfda-d211-a5da-ffdbea210000</guid></item><item><title>“这让我很惊讶，我不知道”：内塔尼亚胡对 10 月 7 日以色列军事基地发生的事情感到“惊讶”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-surprised-to-hear-what-happened-at-israeli-army-base-on-october-7/00000190-bfd0-d2f8-abdb-bff421df0000</link><description>第 12 频道新闻播出了内塔尼亚胡与在纳哈尔奥兹军事哨所被杀的以色列国防军女观察员家属会面的录音，显示总理不知道这些士兵没有携带武器，而且官员们探望了这些家庭</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 10:18:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-surprised-to-hear-what-happened-at-israeli-army-base-on-october-7/00000190-bfd0-d2f8-abdb-bff421df0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列中部发现六岁儿童尸体，母亲涉嫌谋杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/body-of-six-year-old-found-in-central-israel-mother-suspected-of-murder/00000190-c005-db81-a3f7-f29d11db0000</link><description>在尸体被发现之前，一名33岁的女子在荷兹利亚购物中心入口处用斧头袭击一名保安并轻伤了他，随后被捕。警方怀疑她是男孩的母亲，并且她患有精神疾病</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 10:04:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/body-of-six-year-old-found-in-central-israel-mother-suspected-of-murder/00000190-c005-db81-a3f7-f29d11db0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队向极端正统派男子发出数千份征兵通知，引发抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-to-issue-thousands-of-draft-notices-to-ultra-orthodox-men-sparking-protests/00000190-bf3a-d458-a3d7-bfff171f0000</link><description>以色列军队预计将向正在犹太学院工作或已经退学的极端正统派男子发出约 6,000 份征兵通知。军队宣布这一消息后，大约 150 名来自极端极端正统教派的男子封锁了一条高速公路以示抗议</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 06:12:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-to-issue-thousands-of-draft-notices-to-ultra-orthodox-men-sparking-protests/00000190-bf3a-d458-a3d7-bfff171f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>